 <title>Mobile Apps Made Easy: Using HTML and Drupal 8 to create your app</title>
 <link>http://badcamp-2015.kbox/session/mobile-apps-made-easy-using-html-and-drupal-8-create-your-app</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;body field&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Creating a rich mobile app doesn&#039;t require learning complicated languages or understanding how to &quot;compile&quot; software. It&#039;s possible using tools you already know: HTML, Javascript, CSS and a CMS for a content repository. This session will explain how you can use Drupal 8, Apache Cordova, and the Ionic Framework to rapidly build and release your mobile app. In under an hour, we’ll walk through the background concepts required to go from web developer to mobile developer, and take you through the development cycle of a sample app.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-session-track field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-inline clearfix field-wrapper&quot;&gt;&lt;h2 class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Session track: &lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul class=&quot;links inline&quot;&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;taxonomy-term-reference-0&quot; class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/tracks/coding-development&quot;&gt;Coding + Development&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-session-skill-level field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-inline clearfix field-wrapper&quot;&gt;&lt;h2 class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Session skill level: &lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul class=&quot;links inline&quot;&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;taxonomy-term-reference-0&quot; class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/skill-level/intermediate&quot;&gt;Intermediate&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-session-speaker field-type-entityreference field-label-inline clearfix field-wrapper&quot;&gt;&lt;div  class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Session speaker(s):&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;textformatter-list&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/users/rbayliss&quot; class=&quot;user user-696 entityreference&quot;&gt;rbayliss&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-session-date-and-time field-type-datetime field-label-inline clearfix field-wrapper&quot;&gt;&lt;div  class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Session date and time:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;date-display-single&quot;&gt;Sunday, October 25, 2015 - 1:30pm&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-session-time-slot field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-inline clearfix field-wrapper&quot;&gt;&lt;h2 class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Session time slot: &lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul class=&quot;links inline&quot;&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;taxonomy-term-reference-0&quot; class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt